description: This stunning 1+ bed, 1 bath condo is a true showstopper! Bright and airy, this top-floor unit has been beautifully renovated for a serene, modern feel. The brand-new luxury bathroom is top of the line and features Kohler fixtures and Miele W/D. The oversized kitchen is ideal for entertaining, and the unit is quiet and private with beautiful views. The spacious bedroom offers a bonus room perfect for an office, plus a massive closet for storage. This condo offers new doors, lighting and in-unit washer/dryer in unit and extra storage in basement. The impeccably maintained building boasts updates such as newer mansard roof, siding and windows, a lovely enclosed backyard with plenty seating, and healthy reserves. Perfectly placed blocks from the beach and East Broadway shops, restaurants, stores- there is nothing left to do but move in! Open houses Sat & Sun, 11:30 AM – 1 PM.
